text:
The road for parking is still a rocky road.
Nice view of driving range!
Golf map is fine, golf ball dispenser is kind of need to change, staff there is friendly, price is fine (Rm16 for 100 balls).
One thing I like is they have a mini green for people to access.
Nice place for practicing your swings at the range and short game area for pitching and putts. Friendly staff at the bar too.
Prepaid RM200 for a promo and range closed the following week. New operator refused to acknowledge program and club denies.any involvement. What a scam.
One of the best training ground with short game facilities.
